Path: godot/classes/class_spriteframes.rst
Summary: Provides a library of sprite frames and animation data for AnimatedSprite2D and AnimatedSprite3D nodes.

Sprite frame library for an AnimatedSprite2D or AnimatedSprite3D node. Contains frames and animation data for playback.
